node.text:
Today we celebrate @sosobrat !!! On the last day of #pride and #blackmusicmonth , Da Brat personifies excellence in BOTH! The FIRST female rapper to have a platinum album with her debut Funkdafied celebrating it’s 27th anniversary this week! Giving us amazing music throughout the YEARS! And being a beautiful example that LOVE IS LOVE with her soulmate, the beautiful @darealbbjudy 🖤…now this table isn’t available, why?… because it’s on its way to the Brat-tat-tat-tat! You can win 3 limited edition signed prints if you can guess my top 4 FAVORITE Da Brat remix features!!!
#dabrat #sosodef
